Direct Known Subclasses:
ScriptModel
public class CommandModel
extends java.util.ArrayList<CommandModel>

A class that represents a (partial) tree of the document. It's basically an array. If it has members it means that this CommandModel represents a whole block (for, if, ...). Otherwise it will only contain information about a CommandBody at a specific line in the script
